Package model.publication

Class Summary
Book The Book class represents book entities and is subclass of Publication.
ConferencePaper The ConferencePaper class represents conference paper entities and is subclass of Publication.
JournalPaper The JournalPaper class represents journal paper entities and is subclass of Publication.
Publication The Publication class represents any types of publications, which could be Book, or ConferencePaper or JournalPaper, that are all subclass of Publication.
